ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great class for diving into Chinese Painting. Enough students in the class were new to the topic, so the class wasn't at all intimidating. The pacing was very appropriate, and the reading was not too heavy. Sensabaugh is very knowledgeable and great at drawing themes together in a cohesive manner. My only complaint is that I sometimes wish there was more time for discussion.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Provided a possible topic for my dissertation.
